		<h3 class="mul-hdr-rule">Unit Measures</h3>
		<p>
			Our unit measures allow designers to use their desired spacing elements. The baseline grid structure is built on a 24 column display, but you can play with spacing on each side, and the units will always equate to 24. You don’t need any other custom elements to use our grid design either. Our coding provides everything you’ll need.
		</p>
		<p>
			Our grid design allows a greater flexibility of layout than other grid coding currently being used on sites/applications. No matter how many grids you want to incorporate on a page, the main 24 unit grid will always reset itself, so you can keep subdividing to include as many as you need within the 24 units.
		</p>

